# Steam Web API key — powers "Sign in through Steam" (Tier 1).
# One key covers every user. Get it at https://steamcommunity.com/dev/apikey
# In production, set this in your Vercel project → Settings → Environment Variables.
# If unset, "Sign in through Steam" is disabled and users fall back to entering
# their own key (Tier 2, "Advanced" option in the connect dialog).
STEAM_API_KEY=

# Optional: the app's public URL, used to build the Steam OpenID return_to/realm.
# Only needed if auto-detection from request headers is wrong (rare). No trailing slash.
# APP_URL=https://your-app.vercel.app
